<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="262" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,151,1005]" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,943,969]" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin 
<emphasis box="[857,913,943,969]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">basi-</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[968,1077,943,968]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="262">processus</emphasis>
, referring to the process at base of the ventral margin of the valva.
</paragraph>
